text: Mister International 2014, the 9th edition of the Mister International competition, was held on 14 February 2014 at the Grand Ballroom, Grand Hilton Seoul, Seoul, South Korea. At the end of the event, Jose Anmer Paredes from Venezuela crowned Neil Perez from the Philippines as the new Mister International 2014.
